        <title>Tiley</title>
        <item>
            <title>1.0.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>Prompt to move the app to /Applications when launched from another location</li>
<li>Per-shortcut global flag: each shortcut within a layout preset can now individually be set as global or local</li>
<li>Separate add buttons for regular shortcuts and global shortcuts, with instant popover tooltips</li>
</ul>
<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Global shortcut setting moved from per-preset to per-shortcut granularity</li>
<li>Existing presets with the legacy per-preset global flag are automatically migrated</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
